OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another day of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers. The showers are
OL,7,Flikely to be heavy with the risk of
OL,8,Fhail and thunder at times. Windy,
OL,9,Flocally gusty near showers and along
OL,10,Fthe coast. Feeling cool.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers gradually easing
OL,13,Fthrough the evening. Becoming largely
OL,14,Fdry with lengthy clear spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping, especially inland. Turning
OL,16,Fchilly, but with a sufficient breeze
OL,17,Fto prevent a frost for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
