OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,6,Fbe largely dry with variable cloud and
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells. Breezy with a
OL,8,Ffew light showers along the coasts.
OL,9,FFeeling cool.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FAnother
OL,12,Fchilly start on Saturday, otherwise
OL,13,Flargely dry with sunny spells. A band
OL,14,Fof rain moves east on Sunday, breaking
OL,15,Fup into showers, locally heavy. Drier
OL,16,Fand warmer on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
